<span id="freeTextContainer15788288834255679238">I have read most of Bhagat&apos;s books by now and mostly haven&apos;t liked them. This was no exception. His books start off really well but then the author takes it in a completely different turn. Sometimes I feel like Bhagat writes only to get Bollywood deals because his books feel like a bad Bollywood movie. <br/><br/>A very confusing story with stupid characters sums up this book. I couldn&apos;t bring myself to like even a single character in this book.<br/><br/>2 stars</span>
